{"tid":1133711,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"求救！俾牙妹發現我冇著底褲","createTime":"2019-05-01T09:31:07.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-01T23:17:28.000Z","uid":1369,"like":4,"dislike":9,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"f14ad7bd9b9fc9b6a2e1d52218cd72cb96ba27a3","tid":1133711,"uid":1369,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-01T09:31:07.000Z","msg":"平時我不嬲刀唔著底褲既<br />\n金日係屋企睇apink 睇到扯晒其 <br />\n尿禁行去廁所嗰陣 牙妹問我係咪冇著底褲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我冇應佢就急急腳咁行左去廁所打飛機 <br />\n<br />\n出到黎距用鄙視嘅目光 叫我以後系屋企著反條底褲<br />\n<br />\n我心諗 屌！你哋女仔多句唔帶爸啦！點解我唔可以唔著底褲！！！<br />\n<br />\n不過我始終唔夠膽講出嚟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n唉  想問下邊到買底褲女子！！！"},{"pid":"c47a7286fb921082233bba80ec7a26d7113adc22","tid":1133711,"uid":200645,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-01T09:31:43.000Z","msg":"你係咪好悶<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9847abeeb42677818216d9ebfaf4cea83e4ca3ed","tid":1133711,"uid":174199,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-01T09:31:51.000Z","msg":"mydress"},{"pid":"63dd1ebc53d831baabc5ca9054931b404e1b3348","tid":1133711,"uid":1369,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c47a7286fb921082233bba80ec7a26d7113adc22","tid":1133711,"uid":200645,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-01T09:31:43.000Z","msg":"你係咪好悶<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-01T09:43:16.000Z","msg":"真人真事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"11e76e063bad20640cf90cbda593085b35f54074","tid":1133711,"uid":31173,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-01T09:49:50.000Z","msg":"你傻架"},{"pid":"310b5fbd9d38d2c90ddd36cded7a81430ba59b79","tid":1133711,"uid":5190,"like":0,"di